{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 865493036, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 61, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 15:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865492638,45974302,4202]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67118720]真的被恶心到了[/uid] (2026-04-22 15:23):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 虽然突破了 但现在是不是也有点危险<br/>市场上就光在涨<br/><br/>之前突破不是普涨的么[/quote]<br/>主线 和题材都在涨<br/>量价也OK  金融也没拖后退<br/>战争题材没有集体反扑<br/>我暂时没有看到风险。", "lou": 2200, "content_length": 83, "reply_to": 865492638, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776842764}, {"pid": 865509958, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 54, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 17:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "蓝标这个业绩可以啊  一季度研发投入那么大还能盈利  <br/>大A的软件标应该没几个比他强了吧 对比上一年也是增速加大的", "lou": 2201, "content_length": 101, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776850005}, {"pid": 865533463, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 21:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865531669,45974302,4213]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67088624]静观尘[/uid] (2026-04-22 21:02):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:a2:是在下输了]蛙趣，云南锗业的业绩来了...25年净利润就2000万...现在已经完全是市梦率了。虽然说要站在光里，但这还能原谅吗...<br/>商航的再生也出业绩了...全是鬼故事...[/quote]<br/>云南锗业炒的是铟  有研新材是补涨<br/>跟他业绩没什么关系", "lou": 2202, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 865531669, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776864293}, {"pid": 865533802, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 79, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 21:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这波很像之前的17连阳  这次我在14号左右判断出GJD持续进场后就没有看空过市场 属于谨慎的做多吧 不追高<br/>但是做的航天 国算 PCB 电池这些都有很高涨幅 材料目前只有十来个点  还不够<br/>整体思路按之前的经验，放量收破5日线就谨慎减仓，无黑天鹅直接跌穿60日线盘中大减。其余时间继续谨慎做多。观察好GJD是否继续持续流入就行", "lou": 2203, "content_length": 288, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776864571}, {"pid": 865534485, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 10, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 21:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865534296,45974302,4214]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67145444]sentser[/uid] (2026-04-22 21:35):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，新安是否符合半导体材料的范畴，而且硅胶业务也符合伴侣机器人，你看我这次的选股入何[s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/>完全不沾边的东西 宁可你说他跟新和成那边我都觉得对", "lou": 2204, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 865534296, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776865092}, {"pid": 865535547, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 21:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "国算方面 机构已经大量出货给柚子 这个方向我会小心吃可能的加速。但是不再买入，等下次租赁转AIDC的时间节点。", "lou": 2205, "content_length": 102, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776865840}, {"pid": 865536160, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-22 21:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865535814,45974302,4215]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=24978389]GGALEXICH11[/uid] (2026-04-22 21:53):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大<br/><br/>请问利通怎么看[/quote]<br/>你引用的这条就是我的看法", "lou": 2206, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 865535814, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776866258}, {"pid": 865586623, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 10:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "先观察  这么大的量更多还是第一次结账给外面的  行情不一定就结束了", "lou": 2207, "content_length": 60, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776912407}, {"pid": 865590288, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 11:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865589673,45974302,4238]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=25646105]luyifan19941107[/uid] (2026-04-23 11:02):[/b]<br/><br/>那出来的资金进材料？形成闭环[/quote]<br/>目前不是低点，我暂时先观望", "lou": 2208, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 865589673, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776913563}, {"pid": 865592878, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 11:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865591820,45974302,4239]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39161094]堕落的信用证[/uid] (2026-04-23 11:13):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，稀土这个算消息面的利空吗？我记得你说过不做有利空的长线。[/quote]<br/>我提前已经说了减仓。", "lou": 2209, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 865591820, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776914348}, {"pid": 865607585, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 12:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865605041,45974302,4247]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67156308]xenoblade4[/uid] (2026-04-23 12:34):[/b]<br/><br/>早上跟狼大重仓干了一票圣阳+4都没把账户拉红[s:a2:不明觉厉]不太妙的预感[/quote]<br/>双跌停我已经出掉了  只挣了3个点不到", "lou": 2210, "content_length": 38, "reply_to": 865605041, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776920104}, {"pid": 865607654, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 12:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865604295,45974302,4246]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41781022]一位不愿透露姓名的京州市市民[/uid] (2026-04-23 12:28):[/b]<br/><br/>等狼大发言，狼大不动我不动[/quote]<br/>不用等我 我昨天已经说了我的策略", "lou": 2211, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 865604295, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776920147}, {"pid": 865608691, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 13:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865608248,45974302,4248]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62198528]五鬼杀劫[/uid] (2026-04-23 13:01):[/b]<br/><br/>跟的楼里的车的话我猜是没跟着减仓的电池和稀土[/quote]<br/>我记得我清晰的说明的电池和稀土的减仓时间和位置。", "lou": 2212, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 865608248, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776920726}, {"pid": 865609123, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 13:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我目前只留了涨幅不够的那个方向比较多 其他的如果下午没拉回5日线上收盘  我就减出去了<br/>今天如果跌破60日 那什么都减", "lou": 2213, "content_length": 105, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776920955}, {"pid": 865609703, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 13:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在为什么能守在这里 就是观察2点那些钱会不会进来。他们已经来了10天  看看今天会不会不来。如果不来  很多钱会一起卖", "lou": 2214, "content_length": 107, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimesta